'''Gammidge''' ([[Hobbitish|H.]] '''''Galbasi''''') was a family name adopted by [[Hob Gammidge]], in reference of his [[Gamwich family|Gamwich]] (H. ''Galabas'') ancestry. His son [[Hobson]] would change it to [[Gamgee]] (H. ''Galpsi'').<ref>{{App|Gamgee}}</ref>

